  "description": "Add your Wisdom modifier to the damage you deal with any Cleric cantrip.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nThis bonus damage is not automatically included in your cantrips.\n\nYou can add [[lookup @abilities.wis.mod]] to the Situational Bonus field of your cantrip's damage rolls or you can permanently add it to your cantrips by adding \"@abilities.wis.mod\" (minus the quotes) in the Bonus field.\n\nAlternatively, the Damage activity on this feature includes your Wisdom modifier and allows you to choose the damage type in the roll's dialog box.",
